sourcesContent:
<nz-page-header [nzGhost]="false" nzBackIcon nzTitle="New Gift Card Batch"
    nzSubtitle="Create and export a batch of gift cards">
</nz-page-header>
<nz-card [nzActions]="[tmplActions]" style="mt-16">
    <form nz-form [formGroup]="form" (ngSubmit)="onSubmit()">
        <nz-form-item>
            <nz-form-label [nzSm]="6" [nzXs]="24" nzRequired nzFor="name">Name</nz-form-label>
            <nz-form-control [nzSm]="14" [nzXs]="24" nzErrorTip="Invalid name">
                <input nz-input formControlName="name" id="name" />
            </nz-form-control>
        </nz-form-item>
        <nz-form-item>
            <nz-form-label [nzSm]="6" [nzXs]="24" nzRequired nzFor="description">Currency</nz-form-label>
            <nz-form-control [nzSm]="14" [nzXs]="24" nzErrorTip="Invalid currency">
                <nz-select formControlName="currency" id="currency">
                    <nz-option *ngFor="let currency of (route.data | async)?.query" [nzLabel]="currency"
                        [nzValue]="currency"></nz-option>
                </nz-select>
            </nz-form-control>
        </nz-form-item>
        <nz-form-item>
            <nz-form-label [nzSm]="6" [nzXs]="24" nzRequired nzFor="amount">Amount</nz-form-label>
            <nz-form-control [nzSm]="14" [nzXs]="24" nzErrorTip="Invalid amount">
                <nz-input-number formControlName="amount" id="amount" [nzMin]="0" [nzMax]="1000000" [nzStep]="1">
                </nz-input-number>
            </nz-form-control>
        </nz-form-item>
        <nz-form-item>
            <nz-form-label [nzSm]="6" [nzXs]="24" nzRequired nzFor="dates">Availability Date</nz-form-label>
            <nz-form-control [nzSm]="14" [nzXs]="24" nzErrorTip="Invalid date">
                <nz-range-picker formControlName="dates" id="dates"></nz-range-picker>
            </nz-form-control>
        </nz-form-item>
        <nz-form-item>
            <nz-form-label [nzSm]="6" [nzXs]="24" nzRequired nzFor="quantity">Quantity</nz-form-label>
            <nz-form-control [nzSm]="14" [nzXs]="24" nzErrorTip="Invalid quantity">
                <nz-slider formControlName="quantity" id="quantity" [nzMin]="1" [nzMax]="1000" [nzStep]="1"></nz-slider>
            </nz-form-control>
        </nz-form-item>
        <ng-template #tmplActions>
            <button nz-button nzType="primary" [disabled]="form.invalid" (click)="onSubmit()">Submit</button>
        </ng-template>
    </form>
</nz-card>
